{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}
{% block title %} Professors {% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    <div class="container-xxl flex-grow-1 container-p-y">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 mb-4 order-0">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-capitalize">Meet our professors</h4>
                            <span class="text-secondary">ENSET is fortunate to have a team of exceptional professors who bring a wealth of knowledge, expertise, and passion to their teaching.</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="my-4">
                            <img src="{{ asset('assets/img/backgrounds/professors.jpg') }}" class="rounded"
                                 style="height: 300px; width: 100%; object-fit: cover"
                                 alt="professors image">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-secondary">
                                Extensive Knowledge and Expertise: Our professors are highly educated individuals with advanced degrees and extensive knowledge in their respective fields. They have
                                dedicated years to studying and researching their subject areas, becoming experts in their domains. Their depth of understanding allows them to provide valuable
                                insights and perspectives to students. <br>
                                Passionate about Teaching: Our professors have a genuine passion for teaching and a deep desire to inspire and empower their students. They are committed to creating an
                                engaging and interactive learning environment, fostering intellectual curiosity, and igniting a love for learning. Their enthusiasm is contagious and motivates students
                                to actively participate in their education.
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-secondary">
                                Approachability and Availability: Our professors are approachable and prioritize building strong relationships with their students. They are dedicated to creating a
                                supportive and inclusive classroom atmosphere where students feel comfortable asking questions, seeking guidance, and sharing their ideas. They hold regular office
                                hours and are readily available to provide individualized assistance and support. <br>
                                Innovative Teaching Methods: Our professors employ innovative teaching methods to enhance the learning experience. They utilize a combination of lectures, discussions,
                                multimedia resources, and hands-on activities to cater to different learning styles. They also leverage technology to create interactive and immersive learning
                                opportunities, keeping pace with the ever-evolving educational landscape
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <hr>
                        <div class="mt-5">
                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <h4 class="text-capitalize">our great professors</h4>
                                <span class="text-secondary">ENSET is fortunate to have a team of exceptional professors who bring a wealth of knowledge, expertise, and passion to their teaching
                                .</span>
                            </div>

                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between gap-3">
                                {% for section in sections %}
                                    {% for prof in section.professor %}
                                        <div class="d-flex flex-column text-center mb-4">
                                            <div class="symbol symbol-100px symbol-lg-150px mb-2">
                                                <img src="{{ vich_uploader_asset(prof) }}"
                                                     class="rounded" width="150" height="150"
                                                     style="object-fit: cover" alt="professor image">
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="text-center">
                                                <h5 class="text-dark fw-bold text-hover-primary mt-2 mb-1 fs-5">
                                                    Dr.{{ prof.firstName }} {{ prof.lastName }}
                                                </h5>
                                                <small class="text-muted d-block fw-semibold text-capitalize">
                                                    {{ section.course.name }}
                                                </small>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    {% endfor %}
                                {% endfor %}

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 order-1">
                <div class="card">
                    test 2
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}